We will generate number from 1 to 5,lets call it `b`,and then,we will decide if we want to add 5,or not using one more number,we will call it `a`
But that decision must have same probability,50-50.
So,i will generate `a`,its range is from 1 to 7,how can we get 50-50?
We can take for example next rule:
If `a==1` we will not add 5
If `a==2` we will add 5
If `a>2` lets generate `a` again,but that is not good solution,because probability that we will need to generate `a` again is 5/7,we want it to be as small as possible.
So,lets use next rule
If `a<4` we will not add 5
If `a>4` we will add 5
If `a==4` lets generate `a` again

Similar solution is to generate b from 1 to 5 using rand7
